    <name>Clipboard History</name>
    <summary>A clipboard history manager built with Libadwaita</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
            Clipboard History is an utility that keeps track of every copied text, allowing you to easily access and reuse clipboard history.
        </p>
        <p>
            Designed for GNOME and Libadwaita, it integrates seamlessly with the desktop environment and provides a clean, distraction-free interface.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Automatically stores clipboard history</li>
            <li>Quickly search and filter previous entries</li>
            <li>Pin important items for later use</li>
            <li>Can be launched as a background service</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

    <launchable type="desktop-id">
